			<h3>{% trans "Control Blocks" %}</h3>

				<div class= "col-lg-offset-1">
    			<table class="table-bordered table-condensed table-striped">
				<tr><th>Blocks</th><th>Description</th></tr>
				<tr><td><code>if</code></td><td>Do something only if a condiction is true.</td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>else</code></td><td>Do something if the first confition is not true.</td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>then</code></td><td> Writes the code of the condition in one line. <strong>If .. then ..</strong></td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>unless</code></td><td> Do something if a condiction is true. Opposite of <strong>if</strong> </td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>switch</code>, <code>when</code> </td><td>Picks an alternative.</td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>default</code></td><td> Picks this alternative when none of the others are chosen. </td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>for</code></td><td>Repeats a block of code. Do something multiple times.</td></tr>

				<tr><td><code>forever</code>, <code>tick</code></td><td>Repeats something forever.</td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>button</code></td><td>Makes a button and do something when clicked.</td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>keydown</code>,<code>keyup</code>, <code>keypress</code></td><td> Do something when keyboard keys are pressed. </td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>click</code>,<code>dblclick</code></td><td>Do something when the mouse is clicked or double-clicked.</td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>mousedown</code>, <code>mouseup</code>, <code>mousemove</code></td><td>Do something when using the mouse. </td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>lastmousemove</code></td><td>Checks the mouse.</td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>break</code>,<code>continue</code></td><td> Gets out of a repeated loop. </td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>await</code>,<code>defer</code></td><td> Suspends a function to wait for a return value </td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>in</code></td><td> Lists elements in a container. </td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>stop</code></td><td>  </td></tr>
				<tr><td><code>sync</code></td><td>Synchronizes turtles or sprites.</td></tr>


				</table>
				</div>



